            <div class="hero_container">
                <div class="hero_content">
                    <h2>Connecting clients <br> and skilled workers in Valenzuela City</h2>
                    <p>A trusted platform to find reliable workers or showcase your skills. <br> We bridge the gap between talent and opportunity</p>
                    <button class="btn_client" onclick="handleClientClick()">Client</button>
                    <button class="btn_worker" onclick="handleWorkerClick()">Worker</button>
